TePe Dental Floss is a premium quality
column16: waxed dental floss for efficient cleaning between the teeth. The floss is wide and flat for optimal plaque removal. Waxed floss is particularly useful in narrow interdental spaces. Available in two container sizes - 30 m and 5 m. How to use TePe Dental Floss - Use about 40 cm of floss. Wind the ends around the middle finger on each hand and hold a short length of floss tightly between your thumb and index finger. Insert the floss between your teeth using a back-and-forth movement. Curve the floss around each tooth. Clean above and 1-2 mm below the gum line
